    "body": "### Description\n\nHi! \n\nI use `NVIM v0.11.0-dev-1092+g0da4d89558` and I try adding a border for the hover. However, it doesn't appear.\n\nI set handlers as suggested in the Wiki:\n```lua\nlocal handlers = {\n  [\"textDocument/hover\"] = vim.lsp.with(vim.lsp.handlers.hover, { border = \"rounded\" }),\n  [\"textDocument/signatureHelp\"] = vim.lsp.with(vim.lsp.handlers.signature_help, { border = \"rounded\" }),\n}\n\nlspconfig[\"lua_ls\"].setup({\n  handlers = handlers,\n  ...\n}\n```\n\nI also tried calling hover with a `border` option:\n```lua\nvim.lsp.buf.hover({ border = \"rounded\" })\n```\n\nHere is what I get (not border):\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/cd664a80-0337-461a-b50e-7f933cb1fb9a)",
